This paper focuses on using natural language processing and deep learning techniques to detect phishing content in emails, which suggests that it could belong to the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), cybersecurity and privacy (cs.CR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), or information retrieval (cs.IR). However, given the emphasis on NLP and text categorization, cs.CL is the most likely category.
